OL,7,FMr Hett's mother Figen Murray has long
OL,8,Fcampaigned for the introduction of the
OL,9,Flaw, which has yet to get beyond its
OL,10,Fdraft stage in Parliament, despite
OL,11,Fmeetings with a number of government
OL,12,Fministers.
OL,14,FOn 7 May, she will walk from the spot
OL,15,Fwhere her son was killed to Downing
OL,16,FStreet, arriving on 22 May ` the
OL,17,Fseventh anniversary of his death.
