OL,4,Cwalk to Downing Street to demand new
OL,5,Claw
OL,7,F"This year marks the seventh
OL,8,Fanniversary of the Manchester Arena
OL,9,Fattack and rather than spending time
OL,10,Fat home with my family celebrating
OL,11,FMartyn's life, I'll be walking from
OL,12,Fthe Manchester Arena to 10 Downing
OL,13,FStreet to hand-deliver a letter to the
OL,14,FPrime Minister."
OL,16,FLast year, a draft of the new law was
OL,17,Fcriticised by the Commons Home Affairs
OL,18,FCommittee.
